Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.26,0:03:19.70,biaoti,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(733,390)\fad(450,0)}各自的前程
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.95,0:00:44.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,御子乃
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.50,0:00:57.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,灵魂不断轮回
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.61,0:01:00.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,反复转世凡尘
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.44,0:01:03.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,反复身缠悲叹
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.78,0:01:06.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,悲叹于天国为上帝所拥抱
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.76,0:01:07.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.24,0:01:10.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是美好的真谛
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.54,0:01:16.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是他的灵魂却从真谛的圈子中脱离
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.24,0:01:18.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,往更高处迈出了脚步
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.58,0:01:20.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.51,0:01:25.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最后之子的遗骸 不在此地
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.84,0:01:28.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这就宣告着
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.44,0:01:32.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使不对未知的来世抱有憧憬
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.90,0:01:35.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Altair也绝不会灭亡
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.03,0:01:39.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有什么好畏惧的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.80,0:01:43.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最后之子告诉了我们
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.20,0:01:48.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们是活在奇迹之中的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.66,0:01:54.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妖言惑众
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.27,0:01:58.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,绝后的Altair已然是日薄西山
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.55,0:02:02.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不仅如此 Iron C的输出功率也变得不稳定
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.63,0:02:07.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,靠诡辩来欺瞒民众亦不是长久之计
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.02,0:02:10.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,未影 你竟敢大放厥词
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.63,0:02:14.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这次的潜入行动可谓带来了极大的福音
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.27,0:02:17.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你这家伙 让Jin就这么牺牲了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.07,0:02:21.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他为Altair作出了巨大的贡献
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.64,0:02:26.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是值得他以性命相换的贡献
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.03,0:02:28.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你说什么
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.22,0:02:31.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对RareIgler的巢穴所造成的打击
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.22,0:02:34.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,与众真实的夏娃候补的接触
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.78,0:02:41.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且太阳之翼的转世之身也终于要亮相了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.50,0:02:46.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Jin的灵魂如果得知自己取得的成果
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.71,0:02:49.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想必要高兴得颤抖不已了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.26,0:02:57.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊 说不定之后会转生为神圣Altair的最初之子
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.27,0:03:06.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然你真正的目的是…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.27,0:03:10.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Jin
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.77,0:03:14.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他一定不会原谅我和Altair的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,================提供=================
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.17,0:03:29.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接下来前往Neo Stanley的墓地
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.82,0:03:30.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,柚叶呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.82,0:03:32.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs24}校船在2点到达 注意时间
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.08,0:03:32.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把自己关在房间里不出来
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.24,0:03:34.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一直消失着
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.37,0:03:36.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.84,0:03:39.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想就这样一直关着自己吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.70,0:03:42.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我明白她的感受
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.30,0:03:46.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果我也失去了重要的人…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.40,0:03:56.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,柚叶
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.43,0:03:58.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,御子乃·铃白
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.99,0:04:02.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不动总司令
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.73,0:04:09.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个人总觉得好难应付
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.05,0:04:11.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把柚叶·苏尔从房间里带出来
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.18,0:04:15.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这怎么行…现在我想让她静一静
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.67,0:04:20.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在以合体这种联系他人的行为为义务的这所学园里
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.62,0:04:24.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,绝不允许有人独善其身 陷入孤独的深渊之中
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.83,0:04:26.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,居然说独善其身
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.41,0:04:31.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你忘了吗 柚叶的Element能力是消失的能力
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.61,0:04:35.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她因失去了Jin·无双而导致力量失控
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.56,0:04:39.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,继而毁灭自身也不足为奇
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.54,0:04:49.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还是没变啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.56,0:05:10.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,柚叶 我能进来吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.65,0:05:12.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,御子乃同学
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.91,0:05:22.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我在想你多少吃点什么会比较好
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.35,0:05:25.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.03,0:05:27.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 不用勉强的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.33,0:05:29.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就放在这里
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.48,0:05:34.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,柚叶的气息变得好弱
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.76,0:05:36.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我该说些什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.96,0:05:42.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Jin曾经对我说过
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.36,0:05:45.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要我跟他一起走
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.14,0:05:49.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当时我如果回应了他
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.38,0:05:51.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Jin他…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.96,0:05:56.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好 渐渐变弱了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.26,0:05:58.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样下去会…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.89,0:06:05.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走吧 柚叶
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.23,0:06:09.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跟大家一起去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.09,0:06:12.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不…不要 我不想去
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.56,0:06:15.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不想说
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.76,0:06:18.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不想和Jin道别
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.75,0:06:21.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,道别的话不说也没有关系
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.32,0:06:24.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也不想说
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.35,0:06:28.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对Jin也好 对柚叶也好
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.42,0:06:31.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我喜欢柚叶 珍视柚叶
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.18,0:06:35.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以 求你了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.41,0:06:47.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Jin
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.93,0:06:59.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妈妈
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.43,0:07:03.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你就在Jin过去所栖息的世界…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.50,0:07:09.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我对你…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.60,0:07:30.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,终于
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.12,0:07:33.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家终于开始意识到
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.21,0:07:37.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自己身处生死攸关的境地
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.36,0:07:41.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,必须感谢死去的伙伴们
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.58,0:07:44.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,混蛋 你把人的性命当成什么了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.96,0:07:51.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.03,0:07:56.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们难道…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.84,0:07:57.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.10,0:08:01.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们想辍学回家
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.64,0:08:04.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们的觉悟就只有这种程度吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.51,0:08:09.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们可是为了保护这颗星球而被选出来的Element啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.70,0:08:11.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们居然忘记了这份荣耀
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.35,0:08:14.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Mix 算了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.45,0:08:16.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但这样叫人不甘心啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.42,0:08:19.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明都承受了严苛的训练而努力至今
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.35,0:08:22.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,安迪 难道你也…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.04,0:08:29.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要留在学校 连我们都不在怎么行
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.89,0:08:31.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家会被置之不顾
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.13,0:08:36.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,会被吸入到那巨大的洞里
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.27,0:08:39.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要我落入别人挖的洞里
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.01,0:08:41.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恕难从命
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.21,0:08:43.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,安迪…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.50,0:09:31.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,安迪·W·霍尔
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.29,0:09:33.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,挖洞
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.58,0:09:46.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 真是噩梦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.20,0:09:48.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,居然有…居然有这么多洞
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.03,0:09:52.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,辛苦你了 安迪
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.56,0:09:57.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,挖这么多洞要做什么
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.18,0:09:59.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Altair界
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.48,0:10:07.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Jin·无双来自名为Altair的世界
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.08,0:10:09.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Altair
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.42,0:10:14.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,进而 从他遗留下来的数据中判明了Altair的目的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.33,0:10:19.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他们企图掳走女性Element
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.69,0:10:27.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今后与Altair的战斗应该会愈发激烈
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.47,0:10:32.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想必会使埋葬在这里的死者变得更多
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.64,0:10:35.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了应对这场战斗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.83,0:10:38.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要把你们也埋在这里
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.19,0:10:39.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,埋我们…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.23,0:10:40.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.81,0:10:41.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其名为
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.56,0:10:44.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,墓穴特训
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,========================CM========================
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.32,0:10:59.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么要在这刚埋掉同伴的墓地里…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.53,0:11:02.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被埋本身就已经很不愿意了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.57,0:11:05.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且还是被埋在墓穴里 我表示最强烈的拒绝
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.28,0:11:07.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,司令 这果然还是…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.73,0:11:08.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太恶劣了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.17,0:11:09.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,御子乃
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.96,0:11:10.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,御子乃同学
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.72,0:11:12.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家明明都已经伤心欲绝了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.26,0:11:14.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你所说的活简直不可理喻
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.25,0:11:21.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们被生所束缚着
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.49,0:11:24.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,通过与死者同眠
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.72,0:11:27.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们对生的渴望将显著增强
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.05,0:11:33.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,杂念 邪念 哀念 执念 怨念
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.07,0:11:38.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这一切的观念将夺走你们灵魂的自由
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.61,0:11:42.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,并且在与死亡比邻的战场上化作枷锁
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.81,0:11:47.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们必须在这里死一次
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.25,0:11:52.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你说死一次?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.87,0:11:57.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让对生的执着一度爆发出来并将之割舍
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.09,0:12:01.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,短暂的死亡其尽头究竟有着什么
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.76,0:12:04.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用你们的眼睛好好确认
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.97,0:12:07.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真有趣
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.31,0:12:08.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,修雷特
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.06,0:12:12.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我已经算是一个行将就木的人了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.01,0:12:17.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为不久后的死做一次演习也不坏
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.13,0:12:20.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等一下 修雷特
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.12,0:12:22.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,柚叶
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.78,0:12:25.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想陪在他身边
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.39,0:12:29.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想陪在Jin的身边 哪怕只是一会儿
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.20,0:12:38.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这么深的洞 只能靠我自身来填满它了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.19,0:12:43.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要填上这么辛苦挖出来的洞
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.86,0:12:45.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那真是要命
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.29,0:12:52.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不要 绝对不要
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.06,0:12:54.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你现在这样就行了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.75,0:12:58.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你那看穿一切的眼神
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.76,0:13:01.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我最讨厌了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.32,0:13:05.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样就行了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.17,0:13:07.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,御子乃
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.95,0:13:08.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿马塔
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.15,0:13:30.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好黑 什么都看不见
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.12,0:13:35.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多么安静啊 周围一片死寂
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.68,0:13:38.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 还是有声音的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.29,0:13:40.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在土壤上爬行的虫子的动静
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.36,0:13:46.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总在蠕动着挖道前行的生物
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.84,0:13:47.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,令人不快
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.16,0:13:51.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像一群蛆虫从气孔中钻了进来似的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.20,0:13:52.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就这样…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.54,0:13:57.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,身体就这样风化变脆 土崩瓦解似的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.03,0:14:02.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,疙疙瘩瘩的 就像在逐渐腐化
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.95,0:14:08.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,逐渐腐化 随后回归尘土的话
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.16,0:14:11.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Jin与我 能合而为一吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.37,0:14:15.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好可怕 要回归尘土了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.60,0:14:18.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样下去 就回不了地面了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.44,0:14:19.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要怕
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.80,0:14:21.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行 不行
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.95,0:14:24.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要怕 这个洞是…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.36,0:14:28.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行 不要啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.16,0:14:33.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然不行
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.37,0:14:34.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样太乱来了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.90,0:14:35.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总司令
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.10,0:14:37.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再怎么说这也…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.29,0:14:38.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,安静
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.32,0:14:47.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 这群罪孽深重的无翅正在深沉的黑暗中苦苦挣扎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.88,0:14:48.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,神乐
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.37,0:14:52.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你也想与他们一同享受吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.28,0:14:54.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到冥界旅行的乐趣
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.20,0:15:02.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来吧 被埋没吧 神乐
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.39,0:15:07.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被埋没吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.00,0:15:14.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算是乱来 也不能出去
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.63,0:15:18.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊 这是安迪挖的洞
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.38,0:15:21.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我所挖的洞
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.81,0:15:24.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要这么想就不害怕了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.60,0:15:27.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哪怕什么都看不见
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.51,0:15:29.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么都看不见
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.48,0:15:32.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,甚至连我的绝望预知也看不到
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.77,0:15:37.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么那个时候我会看得见呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.96,0:15:44.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果御子乃真的是希尔菲转世
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.59,0:15:48.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿马塔 你是不会被御子乃选中的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.25,0:15:51.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我没有被选中
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.71,0:15:57.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被她留了下来 我真觉得生不如死
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.68,0:16:02.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也许死了也无所谓
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.76,0:16:07.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有Jin的世界 这样的世界
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.57,0:16:08.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要也罢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.88,0:16:12.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,柚叶
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.70,0:16:16.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,柚叶的气息在逐渐消失
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.69,0:16:24.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿马塔的飞翔之力
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.11,0:16:26.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,杰西卡的扭转之力
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.20,0:16:30.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,修雷特的声音 怪炎的绝望
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.59,0:16:34.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有柚叶的消失之力
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.03,0:16:39.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,各自的思念在激荡 如此下去
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.90,0:16:42.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行 柚叶
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.70,0:16:44.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不可以这样 御子乃
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.53,0:16:47.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好不容易变得这么要好
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.30,0:16:50.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好不容易觉得大家能够心意相通
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.51,0:16:53.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.02,0:16:56.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再一次回到这里来啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.93,0:16:57.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.51,0:17:01.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.26,0:17:04.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿马塔
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.47,0:17:09.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,出生的话 又会被遗弃的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.89,0:17:19.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要 再也不想被别人遗弃
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.28,0:17:21.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正在被遗弃
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.10,0:17:25.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿玛塔 在被遗弃
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.52,0:17:28.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,够了 再也不要了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.86,0:17:30.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不要再被遗弃
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.23,0:17:32.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想留在这里
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.27,0:17:37.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,留在这里 像这样和Jin在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.08,0:17:42.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我再也不想出生了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.56,0:17:45.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,孤苦伶仃地活着
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.13,0:17:47.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好痛苦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.22,0:17:49.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,活着好痛苦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.89,0:17:52.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别这样 别这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.12,0:17:56.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家都是笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.22,0:18:01.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.26,0:18:04.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,御子乃·铃白 这就是你所持有的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.68,0:18:10.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人仅仅终结了生命这并不是死亡
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.24,0:18:14.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如同头发与牙齿脱落一样
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.10,0:18:21.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,身体的细胞 意识 心灵都在一刻紧接一刻地死亡
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.02,0:18:24.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一刻紧接一刻地…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.71,0:18:31.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 一旦拘泥于已逝的古旧的自己并固步自封
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.73,0:18:36.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人们就会从巨大的宇宙洪流中被分割出来 四散飘零
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.92,0:18:39.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,御子乃·铃白
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.08,0:18:45.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的力量就是将那些四散飘零的人再次维系起来的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.39,0:18:47.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,维系的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.64,0:18:48.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没错
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.60,0:18:55.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,将禁锢已逝的古旧自己的尸骸为食粮茁壮生长
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.27,0:18:57.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就像蘑菇的菌丝一样
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.70,0:19:01.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在肉眼所看不见的大地深处
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.42,0:19:04.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在生与死的夹缝间
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.18,0:19:10.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,将变得离散飘零的灵魂逐渐团结在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.44,0:19:18.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从一万两千年前开始就深爱着你
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.99,0:19:19.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,骗人
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.01,0:19:25.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,历经八千年的时光 只让这爱意更浓
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.14,0:19:27.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个声音是…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.36,0:19:30.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一直都是孤身一人
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.99,0:19:34.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,觉得别人的事都无关紧要
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.60,0:19:36.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然是Jin
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.81,0:19:38.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是柚叶
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.80,0:19:40.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,与你相遇以后
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.85,0:19:46.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我认识到 人就是想要和他人相连
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.51,0:19:52.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以 不要让生命的流动中断 柚叶
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.52,0:19:54.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有 大家
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.06,0:19:57.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.46,0:20:00.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我已经明白我不是孤单一人
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.24,0:20:03.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们的生命
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.87,0:20:08.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,绝不是只属于自己一个人的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.07,0:20:10.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,生命
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.12,0:20:15.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不只属于自己一人
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.61,0:20:16.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.30,0:20:21.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们的生命 超越生与死
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.14,0:20:24.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在 连成一体
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.16,0:20:29.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,柔软的土地
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.99,0:20:32.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没想到 尸骸就像在摇篮中…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.12,0:20:38.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就像儿时被妈妈抱在怀中一样
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.97,0:20:41.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊 如果没有出生
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.80,0:20:44.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就体会不到这种感觉
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.58,0:20:46.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果没有出生
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.03,0:20:49.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就不能和大家 和Jin相遇
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.52,0:20:54.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没错 洞地外面并不可怕
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.94,0:20:57.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然也有着危险
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.47,0:21:01.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 也有着和洞内同样的温暖
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.39,0:21:04.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要想得到温暖
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.34,0:21:06.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就难免会受伤 承受痛楚
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.18,0:21:08.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使如此…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.69,0:21:12.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还是有唯独诞生于死亡与再生的缝隙间的乐声
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.51,0:21:16.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.16,0:21:18.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家不要惧怕
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.53,0:21:21.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我永远在这里等着你们
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.67,0:21:26.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等着大家再次降生
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.31,0:21:29.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就在这里等着你们
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.92,0:21:34.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在流逝的时光中
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.16,0:21:39.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一刻紧接一刻地死亡 一刻紧接一刻地转生
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.19,0:21:42.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从无到有的一刻
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.90,0:21:45.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正是现在
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.82,0:21:46.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.13,0:21:49.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,将名为现在的时刻紧紧相连在心中吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.43,0:22:02.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这便是
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.85,0:22:04.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,念真合体
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.51,0:22:12.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.21,0:22:14.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,御子乃同学
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.46,0:22:18.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,生日快乐
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.57,0:22:36.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,骗人
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,==========ED=========
Dialogue: 0,0:24:11.68,0:24:14.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从墓中诞生 居然会变得这么强大
Dialogue: 0,0:24:15.00,0:24:16.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也不能输
Dialogue: 0,0:24:16.86,0:24:18.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用一直以来的哔哩哔哩
Dialogue: 0,0:24:18.32,0:24:20.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘎吱嘎吱你
Dialogue: 0,0:24:21.06,0:24:22.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下集 创圣大天使evol
Dialogue: 0,0:24:22.98,0:24:24.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爱的野兽们
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.50,0:20:11.90,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(250,250)\blur3\an7\3c&HBA5341&}Genesis of Aquarion
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.67,0:20:18.87,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(250,250)\blur3\an7\3c&HBA5341&}I remenber sitting with you
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.30,0:20:22.20,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(250,250)\blur3\an7\3c&HBA5341&}Underneath the tree of life
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.78,0:20:25.70,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(250,250)\blur3\an7\3c&HBA5341&}We listened to every fainted cry
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.00,0:20:29.20,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(250,250)\blur3\an7\3c&HBA5341&}Of the creatures there on the day the world began
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.22,0:20:32.24,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(250,250)\blur3\an7\3c&HBA5341&}Looking at everything that I've lost
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.40,0:20:35.60,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(250,250)\blur3\an7\3c&HBA5341&}And almost everything that I've loved
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.60,0:20:39.34,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(250,250)\blur3\an7\3c&HBA5341&}I'll hold them all tightly in my arms
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.50,0:20:43.00,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(250,250)\blur3\an7\3c&HBA5341&}Wondering where I am so please tell me where to go
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.20,0:20:47.30,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(250,250)\blur3\an7\3c&HBA5341&}All of the answers you seek lie hidden in the sun
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.00,0:20:51.90,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(250,250)\blur3\an7\3c&HBA5341&}If I hadn't met you my life
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.30,0:20:55.80,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(250,250)\blur3\an7\3c&HBA5341&}Would've been in the darkness forever
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.60,0:21:00.80,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(250,250)\blur3\an7\3c&HBA5341&}In my wings are the powers of immortality
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.40,0:21:05.90,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(250,250)\blur3\an7\3c&HBA5341&}But by meeting you my whole life has changed
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.15,0:21:12.75,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(250,250)\blur3\an7\3c&HBA5341&}You give light to me hope to me strength into my life
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.00,0:21:16.40,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(250,250)\blur3\an7\3c&HBA5341&}All this time these twelve thousand years I know
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.40,0:21:19.60,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(250,250)\blur3\an7\3c&HBA5341&}愛してる
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.00,0:21:22.80,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(250,250)\blur3\an7\3c&HBA5341&}Eight thousand years from the time that I've met you
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.80,0:21:26.20,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(250,250)\blur3\an7\3c&HBA5341&}My love grows strong than ever before
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.25,0:21:29.65,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(250,250)\blur3\an7\3c&HBA5341&}Words can't say of this time I've been waiting to
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.65,0:21:32.60,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(250,250)\blur3\an7\3c&HBA5341&}Share my love with you
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.80,0:21:35.85,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(250,250)\blur3\an7\3c&HBA5341&}I've give you my life I would give you the world
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.85,0:21:39.10,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(250,250)\blur3\an7\3c&HBA5341&}To see you smiling every day
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.40,0:21:42.80,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(250,250)\blur3\an7\3c&HBA5341&}One hundred million and two thousand years from now
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.80,0:21:45.80,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(250,250)\blur3\an7\3c&HBA5341&}愛してる
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.00,0:21:49.10,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(250,250)\blur3\an7\3c&HBA5341&}I want you to know since you came in my life
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.10,0:21:51.10,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(250,250)\blur3\an7\3c&HBA5341&}Every day every night
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.10,0:21:58.10,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(250,250)\blur3\an7\3c&HBA5341&}You give light into the darkness skies
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.30,0:22:12.40,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(250,250)\blur3\an7\3c&HBA5341&}All these twelve thousand years
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.20,0:22:17.00,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(250,250)\blur3\an7\3c&HBA5341&}I've been loving you
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.50,0:20:11.90,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(250,250)\blur3\an7\3c&HBA5341&}创圣之大天使
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.67,0:20:18.87,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(250,250)\blur3\an7\3c&HBA5341&}世界诞生的那一天
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.30,0:20:22.20,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(250,250)\blur3\an7\3c&HBA5341&}在生命之树之下
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.78,0:20:25.70,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(250,250)\blur3\an7\3c&HBA5341&}两人聆听着远方
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.00,0:20:29.20,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(250,250)\blur3\an7\3c&HBA5341&}鲸鱼们的每一声悲鸣
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.22,0:20:32.24,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(250,250)\blur3\an7\3c&HBA5341&}失去的一切
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.40,0:20:35.60,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(250,250)\blur3\an7\3c&HBA5341&}珍爱的一切
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.60,0:20:39.34,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(250,250)\blur3\an7\3c&HBA5341&}我欲以这双手紧紧抱住
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.50,0:20:43.00,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(250,250)\blur3\an7\3c&HBA5341&}而如今依旧彷徨着去向
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.20,0:20:47.30,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(250,250)\blur3\an7\3c&HBA5341&}琥珀色的太阳潜藏一切答案
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.00,0:20:51.90,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(250,250)\blur3\an7\3c&HBA5341&}如果没有遇见你
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.30,0:20:55.80,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(250,250)\blur3\an7\3c&HBA5341&}我永远只是一个只知杀戮的天使
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.60,0:21:00.80,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(250,250)\blur3\an7\3c&HBA5341&}拥有那永恒瞬间的灵魂
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.40,0:21:05.90,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(250,250)\blur3\an7\3c&HBA5341&}我的羽翼 想要保护你
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.15,0:21:12.75,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(250,250)\blur3\an7\3c&HBA5341&}我就是为了了解这份爱而来到这世上
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.00,0:21:16.40,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(250,250)\blur3\an7\3c&HBA5341&}一万两千年前
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.40,0:21:19.60,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(250,250)\blur3\an7\3c&HBA5341&}就一直爱着你
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.00,0:21:22.80,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(250,250)\blur3\an7\3c&HBA5341&}历经八千年的时光
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.80,0:21:26.20,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(250,250)\blur3\an7\3c&HBA5341&}只让这份爱意更深
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.25,0:21:29.65,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(250,250)\blur3\an7\3c&HBA5341&}任何语言也无法表达
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.65,0:21:32.60,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(250,250)\blur3\an7\3c&HBA5341&}我有多么的爱你
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.80,0:21:35.85,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(250,250)\blur3\an7\3c&HBA5341&}我愿献出生命 献出全世界
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.85,0:21:39.10,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(250,250)\blur3\an7\3c&HBA5341&}只为看到你每日的微笑
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.40,0:21:42.80,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(250,250)\blur3\an7\3c&HBA5341&}即使再过一亿年
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.80,0:21:45.80,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(250,250)\blur3\an7\3c&HBA5341&}我依然会深深爱着你
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.00,0:21:49.10,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(250,250)\blur3\an7\3c&HBA5341&}从认识你的那一天开始
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.10,0:21:51.10,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(250,250)\blur3\an7\3c&HBA5341&}每一天 每一夜
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.10,0:21:58.10,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(250,250)\blur3\an7\3c&HBA5341&}我的地狱都充满着音乐
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.30,0:22:12.40,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(250,250)\blur3\an7\3c&HBA5341&}一万两千年
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.20,0:22:17.00,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(250,250)\blur3\an7\3c&HBA5341&}我爱着你
